{"tid":2405311,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"外交部趙立堅被曝點讚同志色情網站","createTime":"2021-02-12T09:03:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-12T12:10:59.000Z","uid":184679,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"66796a364102e528fef7c1746811fc509e95db6f","tid":2405311,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T09:03:23.000Z","msg":"中國外交部「戰狼」發言人趙立堅，去年2月26日上任第二天被抓包推特上關注日本前AV女優蒼井空帳號，甚至還在情色女星的發文下方留下露骨字句。如今他的推特帳號又被曝光關注了同志色情帳號，引發熱議。<br />\n<br />\n2月11日，趙立堅官方認證的推特帳號@zlj517關注了一個名為「qornograficx」的同志色情帳號，被眼尖的外國YouTuber發現，並上傳影片加以諷刺。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2021/02/12/3438725_2_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2021%2F02%2F12%2F3438725_2_1.jpg&h=fb97cae1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這位YouTuber是化名SerpentZA的斯特澤爾（Winston Frederick Sterzel），他曾在中國廣東省深圳生活了14年，經營的「ADVChina」頻道時常探討中國敏感話題引發關注。<br />\n<br />\nSerpentZA在影片中說：「我找到了什麼呢，這個同性戀色情推特帳號的關注者中有戰狼外交官趙立堅，的確有。這太好笑了，這不是捏造，我們現場直播看到的。是的，如果我重新加載界面，上面顯示被趙立堅關注，你點開之後，這就是他，帶有推特藍色認證標籤的，這絕對是他。他就是那個談論澳洲軍人殺害阿富汗兒童的虛假照片的人。是的，他真的是一個品質低下的人，我們應該說他是一個頂級的戰狼外交官。」<br />\n<br />\n這段影片在海外瘋傳，截至目前，中國官方及趙立堅本人還未就此事作出解釋。<br />\n<br />\n一位網友在評論這起事件時說，我覺得趙立堅這個戰狼外交官，他好像沒有吸取（前）中國駐英國大使劉曉明的教訓。<br />\n<br />\n劉曉明去年9月間被網友發現對推特上一則「絲襪足交」的色情推文按讚，引發網友甚至國外政界人物大肆嘲弄。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3438725\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3438725&d=j8A0%2F5fiWOW2Etl1DmJ%2F%2FD2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=ccec6946\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3438725&h=59c8d5d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3438725</a>"},{"pid":"7b94967dcc7a323a9e3d9ad3d1086f075a4fa5b0","tid":2405311,"uid":184679,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T09:07:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.rfi.fr/media/display/d54b7c60-0ee3-11eb-b829-005056a98db9/w:1280/p:16x9/joe-biden-hunter-biden.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.rfi.fr%2Fmedia%2Fdisplay%2Fd54b7c60-0ee3-11eb-b829-005056a98db9%2Fw%3A1280%2Fp%3A16x9%2Fjoe-biden-hunter-biden.webp&h=a4de51f7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"063bcf629a31a1fd4850990cdd9b9d1a2f22d75d","tid":2405311,"uid":118973,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T09:11:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pT8NyMK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpT8NyMK.jpg&h=b18fbcd0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"195c57f8921e38a64f89dff8033eab54ec366bb8","tid":2405311,"uid":23445,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T09:11:37.000Z","msg":"似係bi <br />\n全部都要<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25330afdc8000b7441691e5092cfa7528dd8699f","tid":2405311,"uid":224533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T09:14:38.000Z","msg":"中蟈性交部"},{"pid":"201947b8b55faab6b8bb5fbb697c701e1625f3c6","tid":2405311,"uid":183758,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T09:15:42.000Z","msg":"支共嘛<br />\n<br />\n趙立堅同志<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dee1b87445062585f248d35f91ca4fade2f8cf3c","tid":2405311,"uid":11291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T09:21:10.000Z","msg":"獨特口味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"091c3d0ddb5a0ad624a95f69294608d0d647b5aa","tid":2405311,"uid":43173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T09:23:31.000Z","msg":"邊個咁大整蠱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24b811a4927acd25f0bd5a0a2d625455a10e0b7f","tid":2405311,"uid":52459,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T09:25:10.000Z","msg":"趙公公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><im